name: Lobster Lane Cottage: private beach
description:
This cottage rents Sunday to Sunday in high season.

Enjoy fresh seafood and bonfires at night while you experience Atlantic Canada! This cottage is nicely appointed with all you will need during your stay. If you are looking for a quiet summer holiday with a warm, sandy beach this is it!

Caissie Cape is well known to locals to have one of the loveliest beaches in Southeast New Brunswick. The neighbours are delightfully friendly and you will love the environment.
neighborhood_overview:
Caissie Cape is a small village with few stores/traffic but a lovely place to spend a summer vacation. Shediac is a short 15 drive away, so if you're looking to see night life, pubs, etc you have easy access.

Caissie Cape is warm & friendly and you will likely get to know some of the locals nearby as you explore the warm waters, shallow tides and sandy beaches of the area. Great for little kids/young families.
host_about:
I have homes on both the East and West Coasts of Canada and enjoy travelling to destinations to enjoy a less touristy, more local approach to visiting places old & new. I am also an Airbnb host!

I live in Vancouver, BC with my husband, son and small dog, Louie. 

In my spare time, I enjoy cycling, gardening, cooking, knitting and yoga.

host_about:
I am a professional Established in Saint John , N.B. Since 1971.
We came to Saint John N.B. In 1971 , My Husbend & I were invited by the Medical community affiliated with Dalhousie university ,  my Husbend a surgeon , myself a Architect.
We are now retired.
We have travelled extensively in North America, Europe, Asia since 1971.
Love to travel by Air & by car.
I like to stay at health Spa Resorsts & B& B , due to our travels we have made many friends all over the world who have become part of our family.
My passion is designing, travelling , cooking , gardening and helping people.
I cannot live without my family, friends,  travelling, cooking & Gardening .
I love to help people, especially children & seniors .
my guests feel comfortable , at home and respected. 
I like  my guests to feel at home, comfortable & safe , during their stay 
They are helped when they need  help and at the same time their privacy is respected.
I like to treat people the way I want to be treated, with love, friendliness  & respect .
My Apts are very well maintained, clean & secure in a very established , professional Neigbourhood.
Our next door neighbours are surgeon , church and elegant executive Apartment owners.
We  all have  owned our properties since 1971.

name: Beautiful Victorian Mansion
description:
Restored Victorian buildings with first class amenities, beautiful historic detailing, and the most comfortable beds you will ever find.

Our Superior Suites include a double or queen bed, fully-equipped kitchenette, and full bathroom - a perfect choice for your short-term getaway or long term stay!

Enjoy the beautiful common areas on the main level, including the front parlour & living room, large dining room, and our gorgeous solarium!


*Pet Friendly
*Housekeeping included
